<img id="big_unit" class="big_u79" src="gpack/travian_default/img/x.gif" alt="Ephor" title="Ephor" /><div id="t_desc">The Ephor is the Spartan magistrate and diplomat. Elected to oversee the city's affairs, he can be sent to enemy villages to sway the populace through rhetoric and intimidation. His authority makes him an effective agent of conquest, bringing new territories under Spartan control.</div>
